 H  1.01  H.blyp-hgh.UPF
 O  16.0  O.blyp-hgh.UPF
ATOMIC_POSITIONS angstrom
 H 0.236783 -0.562451 -0.643775
 H -0.502178 1.016038 -0.048687
 O 0.016753 -0.028633 0.102747
K_POINTS
 1
0.0 0.0 0.0 1.0